                            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                                A typical project takes 2-3 months, though this varies based on complexity. We'll provide a detailed timeline during our initial discussions.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-lg">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Can you work faster?</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                                While we can adjust our process, we've found that following these steps leads to better results and fewer problems later.
                            </p>
                        </div>
