                            <span>Create solutions based on real user needs and evidence</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
